dc_title_s: Hydrography (Polygon and Line)  Sawyer County, WI 2015
dc_description_s: These data layers represent hydrography for Sawyer County, Wisconsin in 2015. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, 'Sawyer_Hydro_2015.gdb'. The feature layers included in this geodatabase are 'Sawyer_HydroLine_2015', and 'Sawyer_HydroPoly_2015'.
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
